    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a rare opportunity to acquire a truly showroom-quality vehicle that satisfies even the most discerning eye. The exterior is finished in a deep, lustrous coat that has been professionally ceramic-coated, showing zero swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections; it effectively glows under any lighting. The factory-spec wheels are pristine, with no hint of curb rash, and are shod in fresh, high-performance rubber. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule. The premium leather upholstery remains supple and taut, with absolutely no wear on the bolsters or thinning of the carpets. All digital interfaces are crisp and responsive, and every tactile switch operates with the precision of a new car. Under the hood, the engine bay is detailed to a mirror finish, reflecting a meticulous maintenance history documented in a comprehensive service binder. This vehicle has been strictly garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment and has never seen a rainy day. It drives exactly as it did the day it was delivered\u2014tight, quiet, and powerful. This is not just a used car; it is a masterfully preserved example of automotive craftsmanship.",
      "price": 48500.0,
